{"tid":242490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無一地兩檢，梁愛詩話西九膠鐵總站要炸o左佢喎","createTime":"2017-05-14T02:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T08:14:10.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a20645d20528ed264c38b2bac81cde39f23f1cc","tid":242490,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"我真係好興奮呀，真係變西九沼澤天空之鏡，文青必到打卡hea足一日！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1330282-20170514.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1330282-20170514.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2By7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b6c693c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1330282-20170514.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8c150a79\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1330282-20170514.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩表示，有港人擔憂高鐵一地兩檢會引起跨境執法問題是過慮，形容只是找理由阻礙香港發展。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩在一個電台節目中表示，高鐵列車起步時比較慢、到站前亦要減速，若實行兩地兩檢，便無法發揮作用。她提到，本港的西九龍總站是以一地兩檢為概念，若不實行，便要炸掉整個站重新規劃，白白花費800多億元，屆時如何向港人交代。<br />\n<br />\n她在節目後提到，港人要考慮一地兩檢的好處，又說中央無強迫香港建高鐵，香港有權選擇是否接受，在執法互助方面有很多可合作的地方。至於權力界限，她相信特區政府會把關。"},{"pid":"a332b971b4259164b6724c8b35d015c07aab80b0","tid":242490,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"扼鳩你起左出黎再話你唔用就嘥左架喇<br />\nd 土共真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e131e2a0b095ebd4c7cc0c918bb69d27c097ad32","tid":242490,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問 d 保皇黨拎番800億囉"},{"pid":"59cfc9f4aea5aa2502d2de8bfa80459783ed4cd5","tid":242490,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"一早講話唔得<br />\n<br />\n邊個半時硬要起"},{"pid":"3d5247179f27